<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>AlgoLeap</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Google+Sans:wght@400;500;700&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="header-left">
        <button class="menu-btn">
          <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="/algoleap.png" alt="AlgoLeap" />
          <span>API Console</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="header-right">
    
        
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <div class="welcome-section">
        <div class="welcome-content">
          <div class="welcome-header">
            <h1>Welcome to AlgoLeap API Console!</h1>
          </div>

          <p align="justify" class="working-in">
            Step into the future with Algoleap Console, the ultimate control hub
            for developers, creators, and enterprises working with Generative
            AI. Inspired by the power and precision of the cloud, Algoleap
            Console offers a seamless, intuitive interface to manage, deploy,
            and monitor GenAI APIs — all in one place. From fine-tuning custom
            models to tracking real-time usage and scaling intelligent
            workflows, Algoleap puts next-gen AI infrastructure at your
            fingertips. Fast, flexible, and built for innovation — this is where
            ideas become intelligent. Welcome to Algoleap. Leap beyond limits.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="quick-access">
        <h2>GenAI APIs</h2>
        <div class="access-grid">
          <a href="#" class="access-card">
            <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
            <span>Text Generation</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="access-card">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
            <span>Image Generation</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="access-card">
            <i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i>
            <span>Video Generation</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="access-card">
            <i class="fas fa-server"></i>
            <span>Audio Generation</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <script src="/script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
